item.title: Past, Present, Future Self - the whole YOU | LAYC71
item.description:
Overheard at the hair salon:

"When you become an adult, you can go back to your inner child self and love her the way you wish you'd be loved, listened to, cared for, protected, valued, encouraged.

We all have the opportunity to reach back and lift our inner child selves up and hug them and let them know they are safe and loved... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/lift-as-you-climb/

item.title: 430: Ekspertenes porteføljer i første kvartal 2023
item.description: I denne episoden går Bjørn Erik, Roger og Mads gjennom resultatene i sine porteføljer i første kvartal 2023. Mads har gjort et comecack det siste året. Roger og Bjørn Erik ligger litt bak indeksen siste året, men begge ligger foran indeks siste 3 årene. Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/61653f7433ffb500132c0775
